parameters: \bustMsgExp[1, 0]\nc<Saki>(Huh? Aren't those the girls who just joined recently...)
\nc<Newcomer 2>Seriously. We're always stuck doing menial tasks...

\bustMsgExp[1, 2]\nc<Saki>(Well, that's because you're newbies... I get it, but
still...)

\nc<Newcomer 1>And she hogs all the events where you can absorb vital
energy.

\nc<Newcomer 2>Even though the company assigns them to us, she acts like
she's doing us a favor.

\bustMsgExp[1, 2]\nc<Saki>(What are you talking about...? The company doesn't do
anything like that!)

\nc<Saki>(All our events are planned from scratch by the seniors!
What were you listening to during the meetings!? )
\nc<Newcomer 1>All they do is spout nonsense in meetings...

\nc<Saki>(We have to meet our quarterly targets, so it can't be
helped...)

\nc<Saki>(...Why am I defending my senior? I'm the one who's had it
the worst!)

\nc<Newcomer 1>Ahh, I wish she'd fail to meet her targets and get sent away
on forced dispatch already.

\nc<Newcomer 2>An old succubus is just dead weight, right? It's so uncool
that she's still clinging to the company...

\nc<Newcomer 1>Exactly, it'd be better if she just disappeared quickly.
With her around, we newcomers can't move up.

\bustMsgExp[1, 2]\nc<Saki>(...How can they say such awful things without knowing
anything? If the senior heard this...)

\bustMsgExp[1, 4]\nc<Saki>(So I'm being called 'senpai' now too...\bustMsgExp[1, 2]No,
no, being called that by people who gossip behind others'
backs isn't great!)
\bustMsgExp[1, 0]\nc<Saki>You don't understand the authority of a team leader, do you?

\bustMsgExp[1, 3]\nc<Saki>A team leader like Meary-senpai can force dispatch any of
you newbies as much as she wants.
\nc<Saki>She's an administrator, even if she is a succubus!

\bustMsgExp[1, 0]\nc<Saki>So you'd better be careful from now on. Especially when
chatting in places like this, everything can be heard!

\bustMsgExp[1, 2]\nc<Saki>Honestly, believing such nonsense... You really don't
understand anything.
\bustMsgExp[1, 3]\nc<Saki>That settles that! I should get back soon!
